<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>اَلْبَيْع<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَرْكَانُ الْبَيْع<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مِنْ أَرْكَانِ الْبَيْعِ الْعَاقِدَان<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>شُرُوطُ الْعَاقِدَيْنِ فِي الْبَيْع<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مِنْ شُرُوطِ الْبَائِعِ وَالْمُشْتَرِي الْعَقْل<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>بَيْعُ الْمَرِيضِ مَرَضَ الْمَوْت<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(مي)</span> ,<span class="c5"> عَنْ الشَّعْبِيّ قَالَ:</span> يَجُوزُ بَيْعُ الْمَرِيضِ وَشِرَاؤُهُ وَنِكَاحُهُ , وَلَا يَكُونُ مِنْ الثُّلُثِ. <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) (مي) ٣٢٦٠ , وإسناده صحيح.</p> </div>